'''Entity''' is an [[:Category:India|Indian]] Esports organization headquartered in Mumbai. The organization alongside [[PUBG Mobile]] has fielded rosters in multiple titles including [https://liquipedia.net/counterstrike/Entity_Gaming Counter Strike], [https://liquipedia.net/dota2/Entity Dota 2], [[League of Legends]], [[Paladins]], and [[Overwatch]].

==History==
'''''Entity''''' first entered [[PUBG Mobile]] by signing the roster of '''''[[The Terrifying Nightmare]]'''''. Eventually the organization entered into a partnership with American Esports organization '''''[[TSM]]''''' forming the IP '''''[[TSM Entity]]'''''. The partnership came to an end on the 22nd of July 2021.
