'''Fight Night Pro Scrims''' is a tournament organised by '''Global Esports''' for professional teams in {{Flag|in}} India with a total prize pool of ₹5,00,000 {{Abbr/INR}}

==About==
===Broadcast Talent===
{{broadcasterCard
